{"tid":2296261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（重開）（千祈咪做檢測）一人留DNA，全家十八代奶野。廢老做檢測，後生比人拉。","createTime":"2020-11-22T10:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T15:51:21.000Z","uid":304769,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d6f9b9736875e2c90f42d3c0e2f1196ec68379","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"今次港共搞檢測動機昭然若揭，就係為左大家既DNA數據。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但係大家仲未明究竟有幾大鑊。好多人以為自己唔做就唔關自己事</span></span></strong>，大家完全唔記得左DNA係遺傳物質，簡單D講，你有一半DNA來自你老豆，四份一from阿爺，八分一from太爺，如此類推。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">搞DNA資料庫最陰毒地方係只要拎到少數人DNA，就可以監控大量近親。有你老豆老母DNA，即使你同你兄弟姐妹唔做檢測，都可以掌握你地DNA。將來&quot;暴動&quot;現場有你、你個仔、你個孫既DNA（例如血液、皮屑、毛髮、體液）都可以trace到你地拉到你地。</span></span></strong><br />\n所以大家唔止自己唔做，更重要係咪比屋企廢老留DNA樣本。如果廢老堅持要做，大家就做孝子賢孫，幫手拎sample去交啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />交之前大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個月前舊po:<br />\n（千祈咪做檢測）一人留DNA，全家十八代奶野。廢老做檢測，後生比人拉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142723</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7789f365fb352270a65d23489fe0d32a787e2a9b","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5606bab8a002266c64e3b0764f8e88912da33a08","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:38:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab620ca093573e5a945ea23a8fa783e5e0192250","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0da6eff6ca18d0bdedad95b087dcebac614da7b7","tid":2296261,"uid":138790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42122b6fdae6d06f0c5871d9cea2d172ae8183b0","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0da6eff6ca18d0bdedad95b087dcebac614da7b7","tid":2296261,"uid":138790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"認真，非膠po"},{"pid":"24c34e006db313fff762e4774938646011aef1c9","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:58:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64ada4a145335debc9e76048702bf8b778a8251d","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32dbcd4f73b93e41a8c38050e7bfbe9df8f6bef7","tid":2296261,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec4b62a0e488f2368006f58af125115ac02e9ac","tid":2296261,"uid":36443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"推，唉。"},{"pid":"8a33f08375e1a9b6c9e05f0f141cb6bb1ec76e4e","tid":2296261,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T15:51:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}